name: Anti-Gargantua
description: This is visually opposite to the Gargantua in the Interstellar Movie .Gargantua in the movie was dark from inside, basically a Black hole, but this one is opposite of it . This is Bright from inside , or i say a white hole ! I didn't put much thought into laws of physics or space .Its just visually opposite of the one in the Movie . I call it Anti-Gargantua ,created it in Photoshop :)
